name: Engine Labs
overview: Engine Labs is a software development company located in Prague -capital of Czech Republic (Central Europe). We provide top quality desktop, web and RIA software development, web design and e-commerce services at affordable prices. As a professional IT-company we offer cost-effective web solutions under one roof, from website design to web application development, from e-commerce services to online customer support solutions. Our software engineers embodies your business ideas on the internet designing customized flexible solutions that are sure to enhance your business identity, give conveniences to your personnel and clients and increase your profits. We will provide you sophisticated web design, development and e-commerce solutions that will enormously improve your current branding and make you prosper online. Development service will help you to set-up your own website, from simple static website to dynamic content and e-commerce portal; your demand will be fully met. We use last technologies as WPF, Silverlight, Jquery, Ajax and ASP.NET to deliver maximal effectiveness in every project.
